wdi2-SH.MED.BEDS.ZS.def: Hospital beds include inpatient beds available in public, private, general, and specialized hospitals and rehabilitation centers. In most cases beds for both acute and chronic care are included.
wdi2-SH.MED.BEDS.ZS.name: Hospital beds
wdi2-SH.MED.BEDS.ZS.source: Data are from the World Health Organization, supplemented by country data.
